The following example shows how to use the  method to assign an account to a team (early bound). For this sample to work correctly, you must be connected to the server to get an  interface. You can find the complete sample in the sample code package in the folder SampleCode\CS\GeneralProgramming\EarlyBound\AssignRecordToTeam.cs.
